<div class="panel panel-info">
  <div class="panel-heading">学生信息</div>
  <div class="panel-body">
    请验证自己的信息是否正确，如有偏差，修改后提交给管理员审核!
  </div>

  <form class="form-horizontal" role="form">
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="student_info_name" class="col-sm-1 control-label">姓名：</label>

      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="student_info_name"
               value=<%= current_student.email %>>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">提交</button>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">取消</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

